front.title: •Shut Him Up Or Shut Him Down
front.gametext: Cancel Death Star Plans, The Professor, Bacta Tank, How Did We Get Into This Mess?, Shoo! Shoo! or Thank The Maker.
front.lore: Some droids are disliked due to their annoying personality. Several highly publicized berserk assassin droid incidents haven't helped their public image.
